{{extend 'layout_new.html'}}
<html>
<head>
  <title>PERT - Products</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="PERTCSS.css">
<style>
      header {
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        background-color: transparent;
        padding: 10px;
      }
  
      nav ul {
        background-color: transparent;
        list-style-type: none;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
  
      nav ul li {
        margin-right: 10px;
      }
  
      nav ul li a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #333;
        padding: 5px;
      }
  
      /* Custom CSS for the home button */
      .home-button {
        width: 70px; /* Adjust the width as desired */
        height: auto; /* Maintain aspect ratio */
      }
      
      footer {
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #777;
      }
      
      .carousel-item {
        display: relative;
      }
  
      .carousel-item img {
        object-fit: cover;
        flex: 1;
      }
  
      .carousel-item .carousel-caption {
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* Adjust the background color and opacity as needed */
        color: white;
        padding: 10px;
        width: 100%; /* Adjust the width as needed */
        height: 60%;
        border-radius: 20px;
      }
  
          /* Styling for the products section */
          .products {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: space-around;
      }
  
      /* Styling for product items */
      .product {
        width: 300px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        padding: 10px;
        border: 0px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
  
      /* Styling for product images */
      .product img {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
  
      /* Styling for product names */
      .product h3 {
        margin-top: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 5px;
      }
          /* Custom CSS for the login form */
    .login-container {
        max-width: 400px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #ccc;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
  
      .login-container h2 {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
  
      .login-container input[type="text"],
      .login-container input[type="password"] {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        border: 1px solid #ccc;
        border-radius: 3px;
      }
  
      .login-container button[type="submit"] {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 10px;
        background-color: #4caf50;
        color: #fff;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 3px;
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      body {
        background-image: url("images/Farm.jpeg");
        background-size: cover; /* Adjust to your preference */
      }
      a {
        color: #e6440e;
      }
      a:visited {
        color: #ffffff;
      }
      a:hover {
        color: #ffffff;
      }
      a:active {
        color: #e6440e;
      }

      
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  

  <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
    <ol class="carousel-indicators">
      <li data-target="" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
      <li data-target="" data-slide-to="1"></li>
      <li data-target="" data-slide-to="2"></li>
    </ol>
    <div class="carousel-inner">
      <div class="carousel-item active">
        <img class="d-block w-100" src="../static/images/truck.jpeg" alt="image of investors at a meeting">
        <div class="carousel-caption">
          <h3></h3>
          <p>At PERTFood Distributors, we recognize the invaluable role that our suppliers play in helping us navigate the challenges of a dystopian world and fulfill our mission of providing sustainable nourishment to the population. We extend our gratitude for your commitment to excellence and invite you to join us as partners in resilience and sustainability.

            As a supplier for PERTFood Distributors, your products and services contribute to our ability to meet the pressing needs of our customers in this harsh reality. We seek suppliers who share our dedication to sustainability, quality, and ethical practices. Together, we can forge a resilient supply chain that supports our collective mission.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img class="d-block w-100"  src="../static/images/warehouse.jpeg" alt="Dyst2">
        <div class="carousel-caption">
          <h3></h3>
          <p> We are committed to fostering strong and transparent relationships with our suppliers. We value open communication and collaboration, recognizing that our success depends on shared trust and mutual understanding. We aim to establish long-term partnerships that are built on integrity, reliability, and a shared commitment to sustainability.

            In a dystopian world with scarce resources, we recognize the importance of responsible sourcing and production. We expect our suppliers to prioritize sustainability, ensuring that their operations align with ethical standards, environmental stewardship, and social responsibility. We value suppliers who actively seek innovative solutions to minimize waste, conserve resources, and reduce their environmental footprint.
            
            Timely delivery and consistent quality are paramount to our ability to provide sustenance to the population. We seek suppliers who demonstrate a strong commitment to reliability, efficiency, and continuous improvement. We appreciate suppliers who embrace innovation, adapt to changing circumstances, and proactively contribute to our collective resilience.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img class="d-block w-100"  src="images/warehouse1.jpeg" alt="Dyst3">
        <div class="carousel-caption">
          <h3></h3>
          <p>We are dedicated to fair and equitable business practices. We value diversity and inclusion, and we expect our suppliers to embrace these principles as well. We seek partners who uphold fair labor practices, treat their employees with respect, and prioritize the well-being and safety of their workforce.

            As a supplier for PERTFodd Distributors, you become an integral part of our mission to provide sustainable nourishment and create a brighter future. We encourage open dialogue, feedback, and shared learning, as we believe that our collective efforts are essential in navigating the challenges of this dystopian landscape.
            
            Together, let us build a resilient and sustainable supply chain that not only meets the needs of today but also ensures a better tomorrow. We thank you for your partnership and look forward to a mutually beneficial and impactful relationship.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="" role="button" data-slide="prev">
      <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
    </a>
    <a class="carousel-control-next" href="" role="button" data-slide="next">
      <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
    </a>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2023 PERT Food Distribution</p>
  </footer>
  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
